{"word":"G2507 - καθαιρέω - kathairéō - kath-ahee-reh'-o - Cast down","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καθαιρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kathairéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kath-ahee-reh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cast down</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இறக்கு, இடி, அழி, நிர்மூலமாக்கு, தள்ளு"},{"paragraph":"1. to take down"},{"paragraph":"2. to pull down, demolish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G138 - αἱρέομαι - hairéomai - hahee-reh'-om-ahee/138\">G138</a> (including its alternate); to <i>lower</i> (or with violence) <i>demolish</i> (literally or figuratively): - cast (pull, put, take) down, destroy.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2506/2506\">G2506</a>, <a href=\"#/G2507/2507\">G2507</a>"}]}